elements.title: Rafflesia lawangensis
elements.contents: ... that Rafflesia lawangensis was previously misidentified as Rafflesia arnoldii, only to be identified as a new species in 2005 after photographs of it were sent to the National University of Malaysia?

elements.title: Paul Chadick
